snippet.title: Ambulance Life: A Paramedic Simulator | Release Window
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1926520/Ambulance_Life_A_Paramedic_Simulator/

Dedicate your life to saving others. As soon as you receive the emergency call, speed off to the site of the accident in your ambulance, sirens wailing. Apply first aid and transport the seriously injured to hospital. Every second counts!

Ambulance Life: A Paramedic Simulator will be available on PC, PlayStation®5 and Xbox Series X|S early 2025.

Follow us on Twitter: https://x.com/TheAmbulanceSim
